                <p>Visualisation after transformation: χ(α)ρτελ(αρίῳ) <hi rend="italic">vel</hi> (χρυσο)τελ(ῇ).</p>
                <p>The <gi>app</gi> element should have a <att>type</att> attribute of "alternative".</p>
                <p>The alternatives could be discussed in full detail in the apparatus.</p>
                <p>Another way to mention an alternative reading is as an entry in a separate, external, apparatus criticus (<ref target="SigiDoc_supp-apparatuscriticus.html">see</ref>).</p>
